name: MySQL5
queryCode:
SELECT
	t1.`ID`,
	t1.`TITLE`,
	t11.orgid,
	t11.MDEPTID,
	t1.deleted,
	t21.spec,
	t1.color,
	t11.acl,
	CONCAT_WS( ',', t11.CREATEDBY, t11.qd, t11.po, t11.rd ) AS acllist,
	t1.product
FROM
	`zt_story` t1
	LEFT JOIN zt_product t11 ON t11.id = t1.product
	LEFT JOIN zt_storyspec t21 ON t21.story = t1.id 
	AND t1.version = t21.version
